This is delicious! I'm not sure what "egg bread" means, but I used challah and it was wonderful. In the future I think I would either break the walnuts up more or omit them entirely. In my opinion, bread pudding is supposed to have a certain texture, and the walnuts break it up. If you like texture juxtapositions, then this is the dish for you. But if you're like me and you prefer consistent and/or known textures to your favorite foods, the walnuts may not be an entirely pleasant addition.

